### @file   .yardopts
### @brief  Options file for yardoc doumentation generation.
###
### Defines/hides tags to supress warnings and provides a list of additional files to be included in 
### the documentation.
###
### @note yardoc expected to be run from the top-level Fruit Salad directory.
###
### @version \$Id: .yardopts 1040 2015-05-13 12:17:49Z piotrs $
###
### @warning
###   This software is specifically written for Cirrus Logic devices.
###   It may not be used with other devices.
################################################################################

# hide tags that will generate warnings from being shown
--tag file:"Filename" 
--hide-tag file
--tag brief:"Summary" 
--hide-tag brief
--tag function:"Function Name" 
--hide-tag function
--tag warning:"Warning" 
--hide-tag warning

# Hide objects with @private tag
--no-private

# Default return value for methods that do not define @return
--default-return ''

# File to be used as the title page of documentation.
--readme docs/FruitSaladGuide.md

# A list of additional files to be added to the generated documentation.
-
docs/glossary.md
docs/LinuxRemote.md
docs/WindowsRemote.md
docs/RaspberryPiTesting.md
docs/SoundClearControlArndale.md
docs/ProjectUsage.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
